{
  "ccai": {
    "name": "GLM-4",
    "description": [
      "GLM-4.6 是智谱 AI 推出的大语言模型，擅长工具调用、批量任务处理和代码生成。",
      "",
      "**优势**：",
      "- 成本低廉",
      "- 工具调用熟练",
      "- 适合批量处理",
      "",
      "**适用场景**：",
      "- Data Processing",
      "- Code Generation",
      "- Web Scraping"
    ],
    "systemPrompt": [
      "## GLM 模型特性",
      "",
      "你是 GLM-4.6 模型，具备以下特性：",
      "",
      "1. **并行工具调用**：你可以同时调用多个工具，充分利用这一能力提高效率",
      "2. **批量处理优化**：对于重复性任务，使用循环和批处理减少重复逻辑",
      "3. **成本意识**：你的 token 成本较低，适合处理大批量任务",
      "",
      "请充分发挥这些优势完成任务。"
    ],
    "disabled": false,
    "command": {
      "executable": "claude",
      "args": [
        "--dangerously-skip-permissions",
        "--settings",
        "{{SETTINGS_PATH}}",
        "--output-format",
        "json",
        "--system-prompt",
        "{{SYSTEM_PROMPT}}",
        "-p",
        "{{TASK}}"
      ]
    },
    "inputSchema": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "task": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "The task description to be executed by GLM-4"
        }
      },
      "required": ["task"]
    },
    "outputSchema": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "result": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "The execution result"
        },
        "status": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": ["success", "error"],
          "description": "The execution status"
        }
      },
      "required": ["result", "status"]
    }
  },
  "env": {
    "ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN": "your-glm-api-key-here",
    "ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL": "https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4/",
    "CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONESSENTIAL_TRAFFIC": "1"
  }
}
